            Gain instant access
            to resources, providers, and equipment
            you may have otherwise not found. 
            %br
            %i.icon-ok.bigger.green
            Exchange science research projects or services 
            with hospitals, universities, research institutes,
            or other service providers across the globe.
      %hr
      .row
        .span7
          %p{ style: "padding:0px; margin:0px; padding-top: 20px; line-height:160%;"}
            %i.icon-ok.bigger.green
            Find out what scientific methods other researchers or service providers are using. Promote
            those that work best for you.
            %br
            %i.icon-ok.bigger.green
            Learn new methods and technologies to use in your research and find out what the science
            marketplace has to offer.
        .span2
          = image_tag "instruments/scimethod.gif"
